data.description: Introducing a charming three-bedroom, two-bathroom home nestled in the heart of Victorville, California. This spacious residence offers 1,762 square feet of comfortable living space, situated on a generous 56,628 square-foot lot. The property is adorned with lush greenery, featuring delightful trees such as a Peachtree, a Mulberry tree, and an Orange tree, enhancing the overall appeal. Two beautiful stables measuring 16 x 24 are included, perfect for housing and caring for your horses.    As you step inside, you’ll be greeted by an inviting open floor plan, with a well-lit living area that seamlessly flows into the dining room and kitchen. The home also has modern amenities such as a smart thermostat, ensuring optimal comfort and energy efficiency.    The kitchen is a chef’s delight, featuring stainless steel appliances, ample cabinet space, and a convenient breakfast bar.    The home also boasts a new 5-ton AC system with two returns for ultimate climate control. A comprehensive security camera system provides peace of mind, while recessed lighting adds a touch of elegance and functionality. A cozy fireplace offers warmth and ambiance.    The three bedrooms are generously sized, providing plenty of room for your family or guests. The master bedroom boasts an en-suite bathroom for your privacy and convenience.    Outside, the expansive lot provides endless possibilities, whether you dream of creating a lush garden, a play area, or additional recreational space. The spacious backyard offers a canvas for your outdoor aspirations. Six Mulberry shade trees grace the property.    The property also includes a two-car garage in a motor-style home setup, providing ample space for your vehicles and storage needs.    Located in the vibrant city of Victorville, you’ll enjoy the convenience of nearby amenities, schools, and shopping centers. This home offers an excellent opportunity to make your mark in this thriving community. Additionally, the septic tank has been recently cleaned, ensuring a hassle-free living experience. Don’t miss the chance to make this property your own and create a dream home in this desirable Southern California location.
